    <section id="calculating-number" class="- topic/section " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="section:4;288:38"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="b:17;288:41">Calculating Numbers of Partitions</b><p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="p:23;288:81">The Object Storage system hashes a given
