</codeblock></p></section>
    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="p:24;294:8">An ideal number of partition directories per drive is 100. However, the system operate
      normally with a wide range of number of partition directories per drive. The table <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="i:4;295:93"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="b:18;295:96">
